docs {
  # Create Saved View

  Creates a new saved view for a user.

  ## Request Body

  ```json
  {
    "userId": "user-001",
    "name": "All Systems Normalized",
    "chartConfigurationId": "chart-normalized",
    "selectedSystems": ["system1", "system2", "system3"],
    "filters": {
      "modelId": "deepseek-r1"
    },
    "normalization": {
      "enabled": true,
      "overrides": {}
    },
    "layers": ["ttft"]
  }
  ```

  ## Fields

  | Field | Type | Required | Description |
  |-------|------|----------|-------------|
  | id | string | No | Auto-generated |
  | userId | string | Yes | Owner user ID |
  | name | string | Yes | Display name |
  | chartConfigurationId | string | Yes | Base chart config |
  | selectedSystems | array | Yes | System IDs to include |
  | filters | object | No | Filter criteria |
  | normalization | object | No | Normalization settings |
  | layers | array | No | Additional data layers |

  ## Response

  Returns created view with auto-generated `id`, `createdAt`, and `updatedAt`.
}
